      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BALANCE THE TILL (4) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Grade 5 winner three back (19.76) at this track over 352m. Better than latest and can atone here. GOLDSTAR CHANEL (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (20.58) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ZORKA (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 352m behind Little Rowdy (20.59) in a Grade 5. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Shapes as one to consider. BUSH BOODIE (3) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
